data.description: SINGLE STORY REMODELED EL CAJON ENTERTAINERS POOL HOME ON A QUIET, PRIVATE CORNER LOT FEATURING AN OUTDOOR BAR AND LARGE SIDE YARD FOR POSSIBLE RV PARKING!  4 BEDROOMS AND 2 REMODELED FULL BATHS PLUS AN OFFICE/STORAGE ROOM! NEWER ROOF AND SOLAR PANELS!  VAULTED BEAMED CEILINGS, FRESH WOOD FLOORS AND MASSIVE FIREPLACE GREET YOU TO A SPACIOUS, BRIGHT AND OPEN FLOOR PLAN!  BEAUTIFUL GRANITE COUNTERS, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, 6 BURNER GAS STOVE TOP WITH DOUBLE OVEN & HOOD RANGE, LIGHT MAPLE WOOD CABINETS AND EAT IN KITCHEN! FORMAL DINING ROOM WITH FRENCH DOORS LOOKING OUT TO AN OASIS WITH SPARKLING POOL, LOUNGE AREA, BUILT IN BAR WITH BBQ AND SHEDS FOR EXTRA STORAGE! BEAUTIFUL GUEST BATH WITH MARBLE VANITY, NEW FIXTURES AND UPDATED WOOD LAMINATE FLOORS! PRIMARY ROOM SUITE HAS PRIVACY, SEPARATED FROM OTHER ROOMS IN THE HOME!  LARGE SIDE YARD HAS TONS OF POTENTIAL, INLAW-SUITE, ADU OR RV WITH HOOKUPS?  IN THE HEART OF THE CITY CLOSE TO SHOPPING, TRANSIT, FREEWAYS, HOSPITALS AND SCHOOLS! TAX RECORD EXCLUDES ADDITIONS TO HOME APPRAISER VERIFIED SQUARE FOOTAGE.  SOLAR LEASE AT $200 WITH ZERO ELECTRIC BILL PER OWNER! BUYER TO ASSUME SOLAR LEASE.  *** INCREDIBLE OPPORTUNITY SELLER IS MOTIVATED!***
